        "## TF-IDF: Weighting Words by Importance\n",
        "\n",
        "- **Term Frequency – Inverse Document Frequency** rewards words that are *distinctive*, not just common\n",
        "- Stopwords (\"the\", \"and\") get low scores; domain-specific terms get high scores\n",
        "\n",
        "$$\n",
        "\\text{TF-IDF}(t, d) = \\underbrace{\\frac{\\text{count}(t, d)}{|d|}}_{\\text{TF}} \\times \\underbrace{\\log \\frac{N}{1 + \\text{df}(t)}}_{\\text{IDF}}\n",
        "$$\n",
        "\n",
        "> **Intuition**: \"Revenue\" appearing only in financial docs → high IDF. \"The\" appearing everywhere → low IDF.\n",
        "\n",
        "---\n",
        "\n",
        "## Sentiment Analysis\n",
        "\n",
