        "- One of the most widely deployed NLP tasks in industry\n",
        "\n",
        ":::{.columns}\n",
        ":::{.column width=\"50%\"}\n",
        "**Examples**\n",
        "\n",
        "| Text | Sentiment |\n",
        "|------|-----------|\n",
        "| \"Exceptional product quality\" | Positive |\n",
        "| \"Complete waste of money\" | Negative |\n",
        "| \"Delivery was on time\" | Neutral |\n",
        "| \"Worst customer service ever\" | Negative |\n",
